---
title: Sweet-Soy Tofu, Chicken & Greens Poke Bowl with Sesame Seeds & Pickled Cucumber
description: We love poke bowls because they’re so easy to customise with your favourite flavours. This version uses marinated tofu, chicken breast, Asian greens and cucumber, with a sprinkling of sesame seeds to tie the whole thing together.

